Basketball
organizations: Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University
lead_paragraph: Jared Sullinger and David Lighty each scored 26 points and No. 4 Ohio State beat No. 9 Florida, 93-75, on Tuesday night in an early matchup of teams with national championship hopes.
